    "It is observed that EarthGPT SOTA specialist models such as CSDS, and T-CNN with improvements of 0.25% and 0.79%, achieving comparable performance with MGSNet.",
    "In the zero-shot classification evaluation, we compare EarthGPT with other MLLMs such as QwenVL-Chat, LLaVa-1.5, and Sphinx in Tab.",
    "It is apparent that EarthGPT shows a notable improvement in the zero-shot evaluation compared to other MLLMs.",
    "Specifically, EarthGPT outperforms Qwen-VL-Chat, LLavaV1.5, and Sphinx in top-1 accuracy on the CLRS dataset, achieving 25.61%, 21.51%, 16.65% respectively.",
    "Additionally, EarthGPT brings improvements of 38.63%, 34.05%, and 24.96% on NaSC-TG2 dataset compared with Qwen-VL-Chat, LLavaV1.5, and Sphinx, respectively."
